  <brief_title>Combination of RAD001 and Erlotinib in Patients With Advanced Non Small Cell Lung Cancer Previously Treated Only With Chemotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Combined Phase 1 and 2 Study Investigating the Combination of RAD001 and Erlotinib in Patients With Advanced NSCLC Previously Treated Only With Chemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
