  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to assess the value of combined treatment with RAD001 and erlotinib in
      patients with advanced Non Small Cell Lung Cancer treated only with chemotherapy as systemic
      therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
